---
title: Carb Smart Turkey Cottage Pie with Cauliflower-Potato Mash
description: We've taken a classic dinner and given it a Carb Smart twist! It's your favourite cottage pie recipe, but topped with a creamy, cauliflower-filled mash!

Carb Smart is based on a per serving calculation of the recipe's carbohydrate amount.
